{"tid":2257861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離屋靚女日日着三點式做運動","createTime":"2020-10-25T14:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T15:45:48.000Z","uid":236500,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1563f5f1dfe0bf50829538634a3a7d94977a22","tid":2257861,"uid":236500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:23:54.000Z","msg":"我老母成日話隔離屋個少女日日着三點式在走廊做運動。今日佢放假種由朝講到晚，對個少女咁着好不滿......<br />\n<br />\n「三點式」示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kpMZS0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kpMZS0.png&h=d213b471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我夜晚終於頂唔順，同老母講：人哋係着現代正常運動裝，唔係三點式呀。<br />\n<br />\n老母：佢在屋苑着到咁做運動？露曬個肚出嚟啦！做運動去運動場做啦！<br />\n<br />\n我：在走廊着運動裝做運動有咩問題呀！唔見你講下屋苑D阿叔阿伯日日着底衫/唔着衫行嚟行去！<br />\n<br />\n阿叔阿伯衣着示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVAgCEd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVAgCEd.jpg&h=5834c43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">老母：阿叔阿伯係咁嫁啦！男人點同呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n原來又係性別歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲老母都係咁，身為女人但偏偏就係會歧視女性，種覺得男人就係大曬，對女人就諸多歧視，性別定型到極點<br />\n<br />\n一幅圖代表我老母思想<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OCZAq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OCZAq8.jpg&h=05908249&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16277c9bb85eff26bd25bd3cb5f4dfe036ce61cf","tid":2257861,"uid":139751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"靚女圖呢？"},{"pid":"39729a7091e39859de2aff205a62678157750e93","tid":2257861,"uid":236500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16277c9bb85eff26bd25bd3cb5f4dfe036ce61cf","tid":2257861,"uid":139751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"靚女圖呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eXiRoU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eXiRoU.jpg&h=42a819ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d83c57b49250c3a48764b17e9a8fdb525c128604","tid":2257861,"uid":342268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"Internalized misogyny. 完。"}]}